{"tid":1801203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【上水勇武】示威者包圍支那客擲物腳踢   支那蝗抱頭竄竄逃命   藍屍疑拍攝遭私了","createTime":"2019-12-28T12:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T13:33:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"180e657731c6b3a4f3829d58e1f96675f5ad57b1","tid":1801203,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3AHvPZVjAihCv_5oLPlAmg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191228a181421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3AHvPZVjAihCv_5oLPlAmg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191228a181421.jpg&h=598d8ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 支那蝗抱頭竄竄逃命  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反修例示威者下午在上水廣場及新都廣場聚集，便衣警察、防暴警察進入商場驅散示威者，帶走十多人。示威者之後轉為滋擾內地旅客和懷疑運水貨人士，指斥「返大陸」、「支那人」。<br />\n<br />\n一批防暴警察傍晚6時再度進入上水廣場驅散人群，並噴胡椒噴霧。一名白衣男子被指拍攝示威者，之後大批示威者圍住男子「私了」，有人搶走白衣男子的手機，並對他拳打腳踢 。男子在混亂間頭部受傷。在場一名紅衣男子被警察制服帶走，掙扎期間曾拉住一名防暴警身上的長槍，遭警員用警棍打手後才放手。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑遇襲受傷的男子由現場急救義工處理，防暴警察稱已經安排救護車。到晚上6時半後，上水廣場外警員向在場人群舉藍旗警告，要求在橋上的人散開，配合解封天橋，之後警方防線就沿天橋向新都廣場方向推進。行人天橋在晚上近6時45分解封，防暴警員現時仍在另一邊連接港鐵上水站的天橋戒備。<br />\n<br />\n大批黑衣示威者拉扯內地旅客的背包及隨身袋，甚至用腳踢行李篋。一名被懷疑運水貨的女子被搶去購物袋，化妝品和護膚品散落一地。有多名女子被示威者包圍指罵，有女途人手上一袋物品被示威者投擲落天橋下。<br />\n<br />\n有兩名途經婦人指罵示威者，之後被包圍及腳踢，有人追趕她們，兩人受驚及後跑入上水港鐵站。要由港鐵職員帶入控制室暫避。"},{"pid":"061a90b9ad5d133fe00c0f43cd62a0578afcece6","tid":1801203,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=058fbb5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n<br />\n【最後4日】全民票選十八區區議會主席與發言人－民主統戰部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800922\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800922</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phk5doO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fphk5doO.jpg&h=40b71bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=058fbb5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n快啲入黎投票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d01a704974e24faee8520af4244789f232b8b7","tid":1801203,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a6bef06377402ba298b8bf78db2a83cd6b6715","tid":1801203,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7b6eace0dcfbdb16e4deecfa129f2831aa2bf1","tid":1801203,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"一再講過要無差別獅鳥走私賊"},{"pid":"e41ab529de1a3aa38f31050f83d12a70b4b0b8ef","tid":1801203,"uid":288765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"中國係咁發達就唔洗嚟買港貨啦"},{"p